data.text:
Thursday, October 4, 7:30 Show, 7 door: Folksinger Tracy Grammer. Tracy has been a favorite here at Tsunami and the whole Northwest for 20 years now. She began her career playing with the great songwriter Dave Carter. After he passed in 2002, Grammer became a solo artist sharing the songs they gave us. Tracy is traveling in celebration and support of her new, highly reviewed album, "Low-Tide." (tix $15 on sale September 1; drop by the store or call 541-345-8986) https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NdmvZNBCx_Qhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Imf2GYV0xNo
